These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
3 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, pony
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family, action
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, tulip, balloon-flower
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is the german##1
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is the owner of the pony##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the italian and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the colombian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Pet           | lizard | guinea-pig   | pony      |
| Movie-Genre   | family        | action    | martial-arts       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Flower         | amaryllis     | tulip | balloon-flower |

