.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid, sunflower
House: colonial, gothic-revival, wooden
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, fonseca, siglo
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the siglo-smoker is the british##1
 2. the siglo-smoker is the person who growssunflower##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the colonial house##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the wooden house##1
10. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Flower   | azalea  | sunflower  | orchid     |
| House   | wooden       | gothic-revival      | colonial         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Cigar           | ritmeester        | siglo      | fonseca         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

