The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
City: hannover, berlin, venice
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person who growsbellflower is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the person drinking water is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person traveling to berlin and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Flower          | begonia      | bellflower      | daffodil      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water    | lemonade          |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | folk      | r&b          |
| City   | berlin    | hannover  | venice      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Sport         | climbing  | sailing   | swimming     |

