 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is between the person who growstulip and the townhouse house##2
 6. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person driving the trike is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the futuristic house is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the van##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
