The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, videographer, photographer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, marigold
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, polish
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, january
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, taxi, van
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
 2. the videographer is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the engineer and the american##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person driving the subway is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Job      | engineer | videographer      | photographer      |
| Flower         | daffodil     | aconite     | marigold  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Birthday         | march    | january | june   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

