.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, august, february
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, pop, soul
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy, balloon-flower
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who growssunflower and the manager##2
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the musician and the fan of soul##2
6. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| Birthday          | august      | february    | september   |
| Music-Genre         | soul    | electronic     | pop     |
| Job           | manager    | dressmaker | musician   |
| Flower   | daisy    | balloon-flower    | sunflower       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

