.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, peach, zucchini
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, cain
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, september, march
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, snowboarding
3 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, turtle
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person eating peach is between the person drinking fanta and the baccarat-smoker##2
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the owner of the hamster is the person who's birthday is in march##1
9. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| Food          | lettuce     | peach      | zucchini     |
| Cigar         | swisher | cain    | baccarat      |
| Birthday   | february   | september | march    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| Sport         | cricket     | ice-hockey | snowboarding |
| Pet     | guinea-pig     | turtle       | hamster    |

