.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
3 different games are played: chess, billiard, snooker
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, ivory, grey
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
House: cape-cod, colonial, tower
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person drinking milk is the person playing snooker##1
2. the person driving the roller is the cape-cod house##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the tower house##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the person who likes ivory is the person playing chess##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the french is between the person playing chess and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Game          | chess   | snooker   | billiard  |
| Color           | ivory  | chestnut | grey    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| House         | colonial | cape-cod   | tower  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 